            "description": "<p>Apis Laboriosa is characterized by a fully dark abdomen with orange or yellow segments in the front. Also, it has long golden thoracic hairs covering its thorax. These dense fur not just cover body and provide insulation in cold temperature but also have sensory functions that detect air currents as well as vibrations.</p>",
